{"tid":1804732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[搶疆]台灣反滲透法已三讀通過","createTime":"2019-12-31T07:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T08:12:35.000Z","uid":109701,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"777897fab348b0107c4bfd5e1a2fee3e5c5f456c","tid":1804732,"uid":109701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T07:58:30.000Z","msg":"趕在2019年最後一天，立法院今下午完成「反滲透法」三讀。未來任何人不得受滲透來源的指示、委託或資助，進行違反選舉、罷免、公投政治獻金的行為，違者最重可處5年以下徒刑，得併科新台幣1000萬元以下罰金。以防範境外敵對勢力的滲透干預。<br />\n<br />\n「反滲透法」自民進黨團11月27日提出草案後，僅召開一場公聽會就火速交付院會逕付二讀，隨即進入一個月協商期。立法院長蘇嘉全上周起兩度召集朝野協商，歷經馬拉松式逐條討論，朝野只對法案名稱、立法意旨及施行日期達成共識，其餘條文皆保留送院會表決。<br />\n<br />\n三讀條文明定，任何人受滲透來源的指示、委託或資助，進行遊說行為，處50萬元以上、500萬元以下罰鍰；若就國防、外交及大陸事務涉及國家安全或國家機密進行遊說者，處3年以下徒刑，得併科500萬元以下罰金。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/amp/story/120863/4259856\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Famp%2Fstory%2F120863%2F4259856&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJgKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=eb80d2c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/amp/story/120863/4259856</a>"},{"pid":"97872300998c655963ba9f7fa8e43a8a4d5fd214","tid":1804732,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T07:58:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德美 聯署 整合<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1804604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1804604</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"2e995fe9d76c9499a5954c7453f8bf0323cb68e6","tid":1804732,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T08:00:37.000Z","msg":"！最後今日！<br />\n德國聯署<br />\n仲差2萬幾人！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1804609\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1804609</a>"},{"pid":"33ce56578788ad6dd9dc563d9a9517933ac3a6ac","tid":1804732,"uid":14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T08:04:02.000Z","msg":"yay!<br />\n抗爭之路 - 所有和理非都一定要做既 2020 New Years Resolution！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eHxOvS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eHxOvS</a>"},{"pid":"d03938be14cac019c4159a7fef062d88b97197ec","tid":1804732,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T08:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}